		"description": "{html}<div><p>Hi,<br>\nI would like to see support of GridView in Titanium.<br>\nCurrently the only way to do something similar is to emulate it\nwith a TableView and internal views, but this brings performance,\nusability problems and a non-native experience.</p>\n<p>Something like<br></p>\n<pre>\n<code class=\"javascript\">// create grid view\nvar gridView = Titanium.UI.Android.createGridView({ data:data });</code>\n</pre>\nwould be desirable.</div>{html}",
