					"body": "Why not bring this into the SDK? \r\nhttps://github.com/nuno/TiCollectionView \r\n\r\nCollectionView on iOS and GridView on Android is very much used in the native world. They are powerful and have such great flexibility. By now, this should be a must have in any cross platform SDK. \r\n\r\n\r\n",
					"updateAuthor": {
						"name": "viezel",
						"key": "viezel",
